{"about_the_game":"<i>The world is old... ancient.<br>The stories about to be told are lost in the nights of time.<br>Two moons still shone in the sky, and the world was prehistoric.<br>Only Atlan, the land of the created, carried with it glimmers of civilization.<br>But it was already too ancient, decadent, and would soon disappear forever.<br>So let me tell you about the memories of those ancestral times.<br>The chronicles of men and women who fought, prayed, loved, and hated so that all would not be lost.<br>Let me tell you, The Barbarians' chronicles.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A SAVAGE PREHISTORIC WORLD TO DISCOVER</h2>An ancient lost land called Atlan, full of legends, mysteries, prehistoric beasts, nightmarish creatures and dangers of all kinds, populated by civilizations with ancient customs and unique mythology.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REFINED AND BRUTAL COMBAT MECHANICS</h2>The art of combat involves dodges, parries, blocks, attacks of various types, counterattacks, rolls, unbalances and blood-filled fatalities.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LOOT ARMOR, WEAPONS AND SHINING TREASURES</h2>The ancient dungeons of Atlan conceal numerous treasures, including powerful weapons, shields, armor, helmets, rings, and so on, which increase your combat efficiency.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">OLD-SCHOOL RPG AND MORE</h2>Age of Barbarians Chronicle is drenched in old school, from the RPG system, which is based on the RPG called Age of Barbarians of the same name, to the Sword &amp; Sorcery setting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BARBARIC COOPERATIVE ACTION</h2>Venture into the world of Atlan with a friend, explore ancient dungeons filled with danger and treasure, embark on one of the many side quests, or complete the campaign cooperatively!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SAVE COMPANIONS AND LET THEM HELP YOU</h2>A party of adventurers is stronger than one man alone, however, remember that the experience points you gain will also be less.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HANDCRAFTED AND PROCEDURAL DUNGEONS</h2>Many dungeons are carefully hand-designed, but at the same time, you will encounter many others that are procedural, offering you countless combinations and making each exploration unique and rewarding.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732130586","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753500/page.bg.jpg?t=1732130586","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753500/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732130586","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753500/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732130586","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,2,5],"notes":"Age of Barbarians Chronicle features intense violence, graphic blood and gore, along with nudity and sexual content."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<i>The world is old... ancient.<br>The stories about to be told are lost in the nights of time.<br>Two moons still shone in the sky, and the world was prehistoric.<br>Only Atlan, the land of the created, carried with it glimmers of civilization.<br>But it was already too ancient, decadent, and would soon disappear forever.<br>So let me tell you about the memories of those ancestral times.<br>The chronicles of men and women who fought, prayed, loved, and hated so that all would not be lost.<br>Let me tell you, The Barbarians' chronicles.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A SAVAGE PREHISTORIC WORLD TO DISCOVER</h2>An ancient lost land called Atlan, full of legends, mysteries, prehistoric beasts, nightmarish creatures and dangers of all kinds, populated by civilizations with ancient customs and unique mythology.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REFINED AND BRUTAL COMBAT MECHANICS</h2>The art of combat involves dodges, parries, blocks, attacks of various types, counterattacks, rolls, unbalances and blood-filled fatalities.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LOOT ARMOR, WEAPONS AND SHINING TREASURES</h2>The ancient dungeons of Atlan conceal numerous treasures, including powerful weapons, shields, armor, helmets, rings, and so on, which increase your combat efficiency.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">OLD-SCHOOL RPG AND MORE</h2>Age of Barbarians Chronicle is drenched in old school, from the RPG system, which is based on the RPG called Age of Barbarians of the same name, to the Sword &amp; Sorcery setting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BARBARIC COOPERATIVE ACTION</h2>Venture into the world of Atlan with a friend, explore ancient dungeons filled with danger and treasure, embark on one of the many side quests, or complete the campaign cooperatively!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SAVE COMPANIONS AND LET THEM HELP YOU</h2>A party of adventurers is stronger than one man alone, however, remember that the experience points you gain will also be less.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HANDCRAFTED AND PROCEDURAL DUNGEONS</h2>Many dungeons are carefully hand-designed, but at the same time, you will encounter many others that are procedural, offering you countless combinations and making each exploration unique and rewarding.","developers":["Crian Soft"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753500/header.jpg?t=1732130586","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257075296,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257075296/movie480.mp4?t=17321305